description: The Deka Eurozone Rendite Plus 1-10 UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the Solactive Eurozone Rendite Plus 1-10 Bond Index (price index). The index contains a maximum of five bonds per eurozone country from the six eurozone countries with the highest five-year yields. Bonds must have an investment grade rating for index adjustment. Furthermore, the maximum weighting per country is 20%.
name: Deka Eurozone Rendite Plus 1-10 UCITS ETF
